marketing: Shell Gadus S5 V460C 00 is a multipurpose extreme pressure lithium complex grease for a wide range of bearing lubrication applications. It is based on high viscosity synthetic base oil, PAO, and a lithium complex soap thickener with the latest in additive technology. It has excellent thermal stability and operates very well across both high and low temperatures.
